name: Raindrops Keep Falling
description:
They didn’t have these sculptures installed when I was a kid. I don’t like them and I don’t really know why. They do add texture and personality to the park, but I dunno… seems to be just another resting place for the raindrops before they settle in their final destination in the soil below.

1704x2272 JPEG

Photo by Jason Charnick
Taken in the Bronx, NY, USA
